Package cdx.opencdx.health.repository

package cdx.opencdx.health.repository
This package is dedicated to housing Hibernate-based repositories or Data Access Objects (DAOs).

All Hibernate repositories are proposed to be placed in this package to ensure their swift identification and retrieval.
